<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
  <h1><i class="bi bi-tag"></i> 物品类别管理</h1>
  <a href="/categories/add" class="btn btn-primary">
    <i class="bi bi-plus-circle"></i> 添加类别
  </a>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
      <% if (categories.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="table-responsive">
          <table class="table table-hover mb-0">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>类别名称</th>
                <th>创建时间</th>
                <th>操作</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <% categories.forEach(category => { %>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <a href="/items/category/<%= category.category_id %>"><%= category.category_name %></a>
                  </td>
                  <td><%= new Date(category.created_at).toLocaleDateString() %></td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="btn-group">
                      <a href="/categories/edit/<%= category.category_id %>" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">
                        <i class="bi bi-pencil"></i>
                      </a>
                      <form action="/categories/delete/<%= category.category_id %>?_method=DELETE" method="POST" class="d-inline">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-danger" onclick="return confirm('确定要删除此类别吗？如果该类别下有物品，将无法删除。')">
                          <i class="bi bi-trash"></i>
                        </button>
                      </form>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              <% }); %>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <div class="card-body text-center py-5">
          <i class="bi bi-tags fs-1 text-muted"></i>
          <h3 class="mt-3">没有找到类别</h3>
          <p>您可以点击"添加类别"按钮来添加您的第一个类别。</p>
          <a href="/categories/add" class="btn btn-primary">
            <i class="bi bi-plus-circle"></i> 添加类别
          </a>
        </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h5 class="card-title mb-0"><i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i> 类别信息</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>类别可以帮助您更好地组织物品。每个物品可以属于一个类别。</p>
        <p>您可以通过类别筛选物品，使物品管理更加有条理。</p>
        <p>如果类别下有物品，则无法删除该类别。</p>
        <div class="d-grid gap-2 mt-3">
          <a href="/items" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
            <i class="bi bi-collection"></i> 查看所有物品
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>